<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="p.petr;2;18|p.petr;3;32C" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">PPetr2,12,3;PPetr3,29C</xref></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Ἀφθονήτωι στρατη-

    <lb n="2"/>γῶι παρὰ Φιλίππου 

    <lb n="3"/>καὶ Πτολεμαίου. εἰσε-

    <lb n="4"/>δώκαμέν σοι ἔντευξιν 

    <lb n="5"/>κατὰ Παυσανίου περὶ 

    <lb n="6"/>ὧν ἐνεκαλοῦμεν αὐτῶι. 

    <lb n="7"/>σοῦ δὲ γράψαντος τῶι 

    <lb n="8"/>ἐπιστάτηι παραπέ-

    <lb n="9"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">μψαι αὐτὸν</supplied> <gap extent="4" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><gap extent="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="10"/>οὖ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν</supplied> σε εἰσκαλέσασθαι 

    <lb n="11"/>ἡμᾶς καὶ ἐπισκεψά-

    <lb n="12"/>μενον ἃ διὰ τῆς ἐντεύ-

    <lb n="13"/>ξεως αὐτῶι ἐγκεκλή-

    <lb n="14"/>καμεν ἐπαναγκάσαι 

    <lb n="15"/>αὐτὸν τὸ δίκαιον 

    <lb n="16"/>ἡμῖν ὑποσχεῖν. τού-

    <lb n="17"/>του γὰρ γενομένου 

    <lb n="18"/>οὐ τὸν πλείω χρόνον 

    <lb n="19"/>καταφθαρησόμεθα, ἀλλὰ 

    <lb n="20"/>διὰ σὲ τῆς πάσης φιλαν-

    <lb n="21"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">θρωπίας τευξόμεθα.</supplied> 

    <lb n="22"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">εὐτύχει.</supplied> </ab></div><div n="meta.7413" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.7413" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-0222" notBefore="-0244" type="textDate">244 - 222 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.7413" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Datierung nach der Amtszeit des Strategen Aphthonetos (PP I und VIII  236).</p></div><div n="meta.7413" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Petr.</title><biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">12</biblScope><biblScope type="parts">3</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">7413</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0007</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">12</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0007;;12" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.7413" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.7413" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikationen</head><listBibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">P.Petr. III 29 (c)</bibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">P.Lond. III 529 descr.</bibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">M.Chr. 12</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.7413" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><geogName cert="high" type="nome">Arsinoites</geogName>, <geogName cert="high" key="Aegyptus" type="ancientRegion">Egypt</geogName></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>